1
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:42,039
You're blocking my shot.

2
00:00:42,799 --> 00:00:44,479
Did your leg cramp up or what?

3
00:00:47,719 --> 00:00:48,520
Well, well.

4
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:50,240
If it isn't Qiao Lili.

5
00:00:51,119 --> 00:00:52,119
You know him?

6
00:00:52,119 --> 00:00:53,920
No. Ignore that lunatic.

7
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:55,200
Jiao Jing.

8
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:56,640
You've got some nerve showing up.

9
00:00:57,079 --> 00:00:58,520
I came to warn him.

10
00:00:58,799 --> 00:00:59,840
Long Xiao is about to make his move.

11
00:01:07,599 --> 00:01:09,200
What a crappy movie.

12
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,560
Vulgar, my ass.

13
00:01:11,359 --> 00:01:12,840
I thought it was a porno.

14
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:16,079
Hey kid, what the hell are you looking at?

15
00:01:16,439 --> 00:01:17,040
Dahai, let's go.

16
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:22,480
Damaged goods who got raped,

17
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:24,519
and now she's hooked another sucker.

18
00:01:24,519 --> 00:01:26,359
Lin Qiuyun, you wanna die?

19
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:28,560
I'll rip that mouth right off your face.

20
00:01:28,959 --> 00:01:29,560
No, no, no.

21
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,040
Look at you.

22
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,400
Hooked up with such a wimp.

23
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,599
Say that one more time.

24
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:35,799
Calm down.

25
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:40,159
Apologize.

26
00:01:40,519 --> 00:01:41,719
I won't apologize.

27
00:01:41,719 --> 00:01:42,680
What of it?

28
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,239
You gonna hit me or something?

29
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,120
Sissy.

30
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,680
You know who my bro is?

31
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:49,280
The Giant Wood Group.

32
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,359
Ever heard of it?

33
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,760
The number two of Giant Wood Group,

34
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,319
Zhu Yihai's good brother.

35
00:01:54,319 --> 00:01:56,480
Xiong Dali is my blood brother.

36
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,480
Xiong Dali.

37
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:00,959
Xiong Dali.

38
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,400
Punks like you,

39
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,359
ever heard of him?

40
00:02:04,359 --> 00:02:05,159
Let's go, Lili.

41
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,680
Don't waste your breath on an idiot.

42
00:02:07,799 --> 00:02:09,039
Who you calling an idiot?

43
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:10,759
Hold it!

44
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:11,759
Nobody move.

45
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:14,080
Women, stay put.

46
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,159
Check the men one by one.

47
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,240
Who the hell are you?

48
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,400
Causing trouble around here.

49
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,919
Know who my good brother is?

50
00:02:18,919 --> 00:02:19,800
Who?

51
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,439
My good brother is Xiong Dali.

52
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:23,919
Your brother's name is Xiong Dali?

53
00:02:23,919 --> 00:02:24,840
Damn right.

54
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:26,560
You guys...

55
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,080
Xiong Dali is exactly who we're after.

56
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,560
Move over there.

57
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:31,520
What are you doing?

58
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:32,360
Move, move.

59
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,240
Stop hitting me!

60
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,520
Hit him, not me!

61
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,479
I'm dying, I'm dying.

62
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:38,280
Stop it!

63
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,240
What?

64
00:02:42,319 --> 00:02:43,759
You wanna stick your neck out?

65
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:46,800
Long Xiao sent you, right?

66
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,800
Who's Long Xiao?

67
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,759
Never heard of him.

68
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:49,680
Not gonna admit it?

69
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,479
Fine.

70
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:52,919
Dali, do it.

71
00:03:01,319 --> 00:03:02,879
You think you can scare me?

72
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,439
Picked that up real quick, huh?

73
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,319
It wasn't me.

74
00:03:05,319 --> 00:03:06,360
I just mean...

75
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:08,120
This many of you against one guy? Not fair.

76
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,280
Asking for a beating?

77
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,919
No, no, no, brother!

78
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,120
Talk.

79
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:14,879
Where's Zhu Yihai?

80
00:03:15,159 --> 00:03:16,520
Zhu... Zhu Yihai...

81
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,039
Zhu Yihai is right behind you.

82
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:23,800
Trying to trick me, you bastard?

83
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:26,919
Don't say my brother didn't warn you.

84
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,960
Wait, wait, wait!

85
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,240
Who the hell are you?

86
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:32,120
Xiong Dali, Guohong Steel Plant.

87
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,080
Let my brother go.

88
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,520
Let my brother go first.

89
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,240
In your dreams.

90
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,639
Guess he doesn't want you in one piece.

91
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:41,280
Don't, don't do it!

92
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:42,479
He's got a weapon.

93
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:45,840
Hai, Lili!

94
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:46,680
Go!

95
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,319
Hold on.

96
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:52,919
What?

97
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,080
Who are you?

98
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:56,039
I'm Zhu Yihai.

99
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:04,639
Holy shit.

100
00:04:04,639 --> 00:04:05,479
Get him!

101
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,120
Hai, you guys go first.

102
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:09,800
We're not leaving.

103
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,599
We leave together.

104
00:04:10,599 --> 00:04:11,280
These small fry?

105
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,080
I can handle them.

106
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:12,479
Get out of here, now!

107
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:13,400
Don't give me any crap.

108
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,000
Go!

109
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:15,280
Forget about me, just go!

110
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:15,840
Dahai!

111
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,120
You're the one they're after.

112
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:19,000
If you stay, Dali has to protect you too.

113
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:21,279
Let's go!

114
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,680
Dahai, hurry up!

115
00:04:23,319 --> 00:04:24,519
You stay safe.

116
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,279
We'll wait for you, Dali.

117
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,160
Dahai

118
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,480
Why are you back?

119
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:56,160
Wei Wei

120
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,560
You bastard Long Xiao, let him go!

121
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:01,600
It's been a while, Yihai.

122
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,360
What do you want?

123
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,360
What could I want?

124
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,720
Of course I'm here to see my good brother

125
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:11,160
to talk a little business.

126
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:14,199
You hurt my brother and want to talk business?

127
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,680
Long Xiao.

128
00:05:19,319 --> 00:05:20,439
He's your brother,

129
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,160
so I'm not your brother anymore?

130
00:05:25,439 --> 00:05:26,240
Besides,

131
00:05:27,279 --> 00:05:29,000
he fell on his own by accident.

132
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:30,720
Don't believe me? Ask him.

133
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:32,639
Isn't that right, brother?

134
00:05:32,639 --> 00:05:33,439
You...

135
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,839
Bullshit!

136
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:38,480
Long Xiao.

137
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:43,879
Yihai,

138
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,920
everyone says you're a loyal man.

139
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:48,800
You wouldn't abandon your brother

140
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,759
over some petty gains, would you?

141
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,800
What do you really want?

142
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,360
All this fighting and killing

143
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,680
isn't really my style anymore.

144
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:01,199
Let's keep things simple between us.

145
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:03,519
I'll give you two choices.

146
00:06:06,279 --> 00:06:07,920
Either you sign this contract willingly,

147
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:11,079
or I sign it for you.

148
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,120
Your call.

149
00:06:12,319 --> 00:06:13,360
Aimin Street.

150
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,319
For the sake of Aimin Street,

151
00:06:16,319 --> 00:06:18,079
do you know how many people you've killed?

152
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:20,439
Don't make false accusations, Zhu Yihai.

153
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,199
A huge company like Giant Wood Group

154
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,279
is completely clean.

155
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:27,160
What happened on Aimin Street

156
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,639
were nothing more than accidents.

157
00:06:29,759 --> 00:06:30,360
Zhu Yihai,

158
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,319
I'd advise you to behave yourself.

159
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,279
You wouldn't want

160
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,240
any more accidents to happen, would you?

161
00:06:39,439 --> 00:06:40,120
Dahai,

162
00:06:40,879 --> 00:06:42,160
we can't beat him.

163
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,120
Dahai!

164
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:45,240
Don't worry about me.

165
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:55,920
What's so funny?

166
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:56,759
Come to your senses?

167
00:06:58,319 --> 00:06:59,079
Yeah, I have.

168
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:00,959
Then sign it.

169
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:07,560
I'm so glad I signed for 52 back then.

170
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:09,519
Otherwise, you'd have gotten your way.

171
00:07:09,839 --> 00:07:10,839
Glad, huh?

172
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,040
Shouldn't you be regretting it instead?

173
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,040
Otherwise, your brother

174
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,360
wouldn't be in this state now.

175
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:18,279
Do you know why Director Ge

176
00:07:18,279 --> 00:07:19,600
gave Aimin Street to me

177
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,519
instead of you?

178
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:22,439
Come on,

179
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:24,199
let's hear it.

180
00:07:29,759 --> 00:07:30,399
Dad,

181
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,399
why bother talking with Long Xiao?

182
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,680
I also wanted to bet everything

183
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,319
on Zhu Yihai.

184
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,680
But he can't come up with six million.

185
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,199
Then take a look at this.

186
00:07:42,759 --> 00:07:43,800
Do you know

187
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,160
that everything happening on Aimin Street

188
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:46,800
is all connected to Long Xiao?

189
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,959
This was all Long Xiao's doing.

190
00:07:56,439 --> 00:07:59,519
Good thing I didn't sign with Long Xiao.

191
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:01,399
Otherwise, we'd be in deep trouble.

192
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,040
Why would you

193
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,160
sell it cheap to Zhu Yihai then?

194
00:08:05,439 --> 00:08:06,519
He's the only one

195
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:09,639
truly trying to find a way out for our plant.

196
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,600
When the plant gets demolished,

197
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:13,680
I'll open a foot massage parlor on Aimin Street.

198
00:08:13,959 --> 00:08:16,319
Everyone from the night market can come to my place.

199
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:17,519
You mean

200
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,959
you'd let our plant workers

201
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,079
all come work for you?

202
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:22,319
Right, come work at my place.

203
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,759
That's why I feel at ease

204
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:25,879
giving the plant to him.

205
00:08:27,439 --> 00:08:28,600
How interesting.

206
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,839
I schemed with that old man forever,

207
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:34,639
and your foot parlor beat me to it.

208
00:08:34,879 --> 00:08:37,080
Because you've done too many bad things.

209
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,679
If you'd cared even a little for these people,

210
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:41,559
I would've signed that contract.

211
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,600
But now?

212
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,559
Let me tell you,

213
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:47,399
no way in hell.

214
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,200
Really?

215
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,919
What if I cripple him?

216
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,480
I dare you to touch him.

217
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,440
Dali!

218
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:58,679
Hai.

219
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:01,559
I'm late.

220
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,279
Long Xiao,

221
00:09:06,879 --> 00:09:08,759
let Wei Wei go!

222
00:09:08,759 --> 00:09:09,240
Dali!

223
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:11,200
Dali!

224
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,519
Oh, Xiong Dali, Xiong Dali.

225
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:17,919
You should really learn from Dahai.

226
00:09:18,399 --> 00:09:20,639
Look how obedient he became after one stint in jail.

227
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:22,360
Speaking of that prison time,

228
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,759
I actually set that up too.

229
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:27,000
You thought you saved me?

230
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,879
It was all just a plan to lure you in.

231
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,159
After all, Zhu Yihai

232
00:09:32,799 --> 00:09:34,879
is famously loyal far and wide.

233
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:36,919
Why would you do this?

234
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:38,440
Why?

235
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:40,200
Without you,

236
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:42,360
who'd deal with Ge Zhendong for me?

237
00:09:45,399 --> 00:09:45,919
Alright, alright.

238
00:09:45,919 --> 00:09:46,960
Let's cut the crap.

239
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,639
I'm running out of patience.

240
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,120
Sign it or not?

241
00:09:50,399 --> 00:09:51,240
Dahai,

242
00:09:52,399 --> 00:09:53,879
don't waste words on him.

243
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:54,360
Wei Wei,

244
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,279
when adults are talking,

245
00:09:58,639 --> 00:10:00,399
kids don't butt in.

246
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:03,799
My eye!

247
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:04,320
Long Xiao!

248
00:10:06,799 --> 00:10:08,240
I'll kill you!

249
00:10:29,879 --> 00:10:32,080
Long Xiao, you're despicable.

250
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,080
You don't want to sign it?

251
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:44,600
Then I'll have to sign it for you.

252
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:51,679
See?

253
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,320
Such a simple little thing.

254
00:10:55,639 --> 00:10:57,000
And you turned it into this mess.

255
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:02,200
Yihai!

256
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,240
All of you, stay right there!

257
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:04,559
Long Xiao!

258
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,559
I've already called the cops.

259
00:11:05,559 --> 00:11:06,159
Let go!

260
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:08,919
Dahai! Dahai!

261
00:11:10,039 --> 00:11:11,000
Dahai!

262
00:11:12,639 --> 00:11:13,600
Dahai!

263
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:15,960
Wei Wei! Wei Wei!

264
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,200
Intentional assault.

265
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:19,840
Come with me.

266
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:20,720
Dao Balian.

267
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:23,360
You really think you're something, huh?

268
00:11:24,639 --> 00:11:25,600
Get the hell out!

269
00:11:29,399 --> 00:11:31,799
I'm still the Head of Security, you know.

270
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,320
Cuff him.

271
00:11:44,519 --> 00:11:45,320
Huilian.

272
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:47,639
What did you do to her?

273
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,159
Take a guess.

274
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:53,519
Move!

275
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:56,759
Hurry!

276
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:57,960
Call an ambulance!

277
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,559
Hurry up, come on!

